    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/9eff91c4e3dae38ded837dae2fbaf608.avif?t=1745569229\" width=630 height=80 /></span><br><br>《战斗躯壳》是一款融合战斗战甲、意识漫游、数据模拟、AI机械元素的科幻题材Roguelike类游戏。<br><br>在不远的将来，一家研究AI技术的公司正在进行一种将人的意识存储在U盘里的实验。作为玩家的你，被强制的投入了实验中，通过一次次战斗、死亡，达成逃出整个实验计划的目的。<br><br>在游戏中玩家将用TPS的游戏方式来进行战斗演算。在战斗中你将面对不同的抉择：初始选择的躯壳，过程中获得的技能词条模块，规划下步行进路径，携带的枪械等等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/5ca30cb050aa7f48b5f4889b0fd59452.poster.avif?t=1745569229\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/5ca30cb050aa7f48b5f4889b0fd59452.webm?t=1745569229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/5ca30cb050aa7f48b5f4889b0fd59452.mp4?t=1745569229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/d37e53b1243a6419a61dc3662fdc1815.avif?t=1745569229\" width=630 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>随机生成的关卡——每一次战斗都是不同的冒险<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/fecf313c033a7f79be972799d23b6483.poster.avif?t=1745569229\" width=510 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/fecf313c033a7f79be972799d23b6483.webm?t=1745569229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754500/extras/fecf313c033a7f79be972799d23b6483.mp4?t=1745569229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></